Dependency=Income: # Description: Federal poverty level of the household occupying the dwelling unit.
# Source: 2019-5yrs Public Use Microdata Samples (PUMS). IPUMS USA, University of Minnesota, www.ipums.org.

# Assumption: % Federal Poverty Level is calculated using annual household income in 2019USD (continuous, not binned) from 2019-5yrs PUMS data and 2019 Federal Poverty Lines for contiguous US, where the FPL threshold for 1-occupant household is $12490 and $4420 for every additional person in the household.
